---
<section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-900 to-slate-800" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/WebPageElement">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight text-slate-100" itemprop="headline">
        抽檢 2% 是運氣，<span class="text-blue-400">全檢 100%</span> 才是實力
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed" itemprop="description">
        別再用運氣管理客服。用 AI 實現 100% 全量質檢，精準揪出每一次失誤，釋放 80% 的 QA 人力成本。
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-4">
        <a href="#contact" class="px-8 py-4 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-blue-700 transition-all text-base md:text-lg shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/20">
          免費開始檢測
        </a>
        <a href="#product" class="px-8 py-4 border-2 border-slate-600 text-slate-200 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-slate-800 hover:border-slate-500 transition text-base md:text-lg">
          查看實際演示
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6 pb-4 border-b border-slate-200">
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold text-slate-900 text-lg">客服品質管理 Dashboard</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">100% 全量質檢中</div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-green-50 rounded-full border border-green-200">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-500 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
            <span class="text-xs text-green-700 font-medium">即時監控</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3" id="dashboardDemo">
          <!-- 統計卡片 -->
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-lg p-3 border border-slate-200">
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-1">總對話數</div>
              <div class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900">7,702</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-lg p-3 border border-slate-200">
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-1">檢測中</div>
              <div class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-600">1,234</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-lg p-3 border border-slate-200">
              <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-1">錯誤數</div>
              <div class="text-xl font-bold text-orange-600">28</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 評分列表 -->
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-green-50 rounded-lg border border-green-200">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">客服 A - 對話 #1234</div>
                  <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">語氣友善，回應得當</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm font-bold text-green-600">✓ 通過</div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg border border-yellow-200">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-yellow-500 rounded-full"></div>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">客服 B - 對話 #1235</div>
                  <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">回應較為簡短，建議補充說明</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm font-bold text-yellow-600">⚠ 待改善</div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-red-50 rounded-lg border border-red-200">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-red-500 rounded-full"></div>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">客服 C - 對話 #1236</div>
                  <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">偵測到不耐煩語氣</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm font-bold text-red-600">✗ 不合格</div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-green-50 rounded-lg border border-green-200">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
                <div>
                  <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">客服 D - 對話 #1237</div>
                  <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">專業且具同理心</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="text-sm font-bold text-green-600">✓ 通過</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<style>
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% {
      opacity: 1;
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 0.5;
    }
  }
  
  .animate-pulse {
    animation: pulse 2s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite;
  }
</style>

